window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Darkness will strike again. </b></p> <p>The last time Carl, Volka, and 6T9 fought the Dark, 6T9 failed Volka. If he wants her and all the carbon-based life forms that he loves to survive, he needs to change. Change is as easy as flipping a switch for an android, but dealing with the consequences is not so simple.&nbsp;</p> <p>In order to save Volka, he’ll have to give up a part of himself that Volka adores. He’ll need to become something an innocent, peace-loving sex ‘bot was never designed to be...something he despises.&nbsp;</p> <p>To save Volka and the galaxy he’ll need to become Android General 1.</p>"; 
